{"tid":855452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小米手環 3 心率偵測有誤 廁紙亦測出心跳","createTime":"2018-10-10T05:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T15:31:30.000Z","uid":72009,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"12710190aad27669b2f51e2fca669bc1c9223c24","tid":855452,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"很多人佩戴健康手環，都是希望能夠統計每天行走的步數、計算運動量和量度心跳，至於數據的誤差多與少，除非消費者以醫學用裝置比對，否則一般都無法知道。最近有大陸網民就進行了一個有趣的實驗，以一卷白色的廁紙去測試小米手環 3 的心率偵測裝置，結果出人意料。<br />\n<br />\n網民發現就算將小米手環 3 綁在一卷廁紙，心率感應器仍然偵測到心跳，而且讀數甚至比用戶本身更高，該網民在微博公開結果後，引發不少討論。有 Fitbit Versa 運動追蹤手錶的用戶，進行同樣測試，結果手錶沒有任何反應。為了進一步求證，網站 GizmoChina 的兩名編輯分別以兩卷廁紙和兩隻小米手環 3 進行測試，結果是一隻馬上讀到心跳，另一隻則在記者輕敲廁紙筒後成功讀取。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1010-5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1010-5a.jpg&h=2f1ba3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/10/mi-band-3-heart-rate-sensors-credibility-in-the-spotlight-gets-a-reading-for-tissue-paper/life-tech/sport-tech/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2Fmi-band-3-heart-rate-sensors-credibility-in-the-spotlight-gets-a-reading-for-tissue-paper%2Flife-tech%2Fsport-tech%2Famp%2F&d=VvRda%2FphPWYygqpmMXAMCTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bb930725\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/10/mi-band-3-heart-rate-sensors-credibility-in-the-spotlight-gets-a-reading-for-tissue-paper/life-tech/sport-tech/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7a2dd7553d1198197272d76b45e7880ab0324d","tid":855452,"uid":52006,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"萬物皆有生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52cd6d9fd38f52f49187e84194235ac06746fe4","tid":855452,"uid":213441,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"rep